Package: dataLGBT
Title: Brazilian Sexual and Gender Minorities Death Reporting Tool
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Natan", "Nascimento de Oliveira", 
           email = "nat_oliveira98@hotmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for processing, record linkage, and reporting of mortality and violence data related to sexual and gender minorities (SGM) in Brazil. The package standardizes variables from health information systems such as SIM and SINAN, supports probabilistic linkage workflows, and generates epidemiological indicators and automated reports, including burden of disease measures and temporal analyses.
